      <string id="ng_showhostinfo_display">Show Computer Info on Banner (NetBannerNG)</string>
      <string id="ng_showhostinfo_help">Controls host information text (machine name, user, IP) on banners. Disabled policy state forces the host information to be hidden. Default is disabled when managed by GPO.</string>
      <string id="ng_enablebottombanner_display">Enable Bottom Banner (NetBannerNG)</string>
      <string id="ng_enablebottombanner_help">When enabled, renders a full bottom banner matching the top banner. This setting is independent from Disable Borders policy.</string>

